name: o_god_the_mail_06
description:
What does this mean - is it urgent? Is it actually urgent or am I being fooled? These envelopes just pile up and it takes time and energy to process everything and I just feel like I don't have it in me to serve this little stack of paper. Am I forgetting something again? O god, the mail.

Part 6 of a series begun on knownorigin.io
